# README title

The top-level [`README.md`](../README.md) H1 must stay **`# KBee`**, not `# kbee`.

The repo directory is `kbee` (lowercase); the product/project name in prose is
**KBee**. Do not “normalize” the title to lowercase when editing README or
running formatters.
